{"tid":2056180,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞] 粵語長片 (原：粵語殘片 - 陳奕迅)","createTime":"2020-06-08T13:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T07:00:12.000Z","uid":257847,"like":80,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"c09173a42425147ba90176356437024d01e798d0","tid":2056180,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:18:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">粵語長片</span><br />\n原曲：粵語殘片<br />\n原唱：陳奕迅<br />\n原詞：周博賢    <br />\n作曲：陳奕迅/C.Y.Kong<br />\n<br />\n回憶某日 海富佈密 黑衫口罩標幟<br />\n圍困對歭 當天竟奢求暴政遏止<br />\n從那陣時 決心展翅 進入這大廳塗污國恥<br />\n逆權極致 未停在始<br />\n<br />\n想某夜 西鐵變事 警黑勾結宰弑<br />\n奇怪詫異 看新聞怎會白了絲<br />\n亡了法治 痛心失意 某夜於路面放低座椅<br />\n務求嘗試 拋開憤熾<br />\n<br />\n最後沿路截的士<br />\n往旺角必經太子<br />\n刹那間收到這短訊大件事<br />\n<br />\n當天那動人鬧市 在腦海劃成漣漪<br />\n壯麗旗幟 硝煙𥚃翻起往事<br />\n頓然寂爾 再想起那男孩子<br />\n浴血亦如斯 拉上面罩未怕蕀刺<br />\n<br />\n於某日 開拆禮物 身邊好友得知<br />\n朋友致電 胸口很失儀被送醫<br />\n留意告示 迅速草擬 以後需看到鼻子露齒<br />\n莫名男子 相當介意<br />\n<br />\n吐露紅藍無休止<br />\n理大那位魔法師<br />\n刹那間香港彷彿也大件事<br />\n<br />\n今天那動人鬧市 在腦海劃成漣漪<br />\n壯麗旗幟 硝煙𥚃翻起往事<br />\n頓然寂爾 再想起那男孩子<br />\n浴血亦如斯 拉上面罩未怕蕀刺<br />\n<br />\n在絕望窘況當中找到反抗的意義<br />\n為願望現在政制要高舉兩手撕<br />\n要創自由歷史<br />\n<br />\n請謹記日期地址 若結果未能如詩<br />\n亦能誠摯 執手說一些往事<br />\n但求在意 那小姐與男孩子<br />\n聚傘下靠倚 可記敘故事再一次<br />\n<br />\n小弟見抗爭運動邁向一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />改咗首詞去紀錄下當中既一啲片段<br />\n希望大家欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n=======================================================================<br />\n之前既改詞<br />\n<br />\n[改詞］約誓 （原：償還 - 王菲）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2049167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2049167</a><br />\n<br />\n支國失調 (原:：思覺失調 - 劉浩龍)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2053677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2053677</a>"},{"pid":"2e0e9dac4fa0924ee81f7aecb513cdb67d46add8","tid":2056180,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:21:32.000Z","msg":"唔記得放改歌台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819ca2d7a287628f77637c7024518d5f3b0be1d5","tid":2056180,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇人睇"},{"pid":"acf90df324322a4ad1e4cabc600a2fda0db54e4e","tid":2056180,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:00:02.000Z","msg":"冇力照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3690c789fc057bd18d71fa64e23a207c0b53ad","tid":2056180,"uid":25112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:00:27.000Z","msg":"Pish 呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d55625d644530bd2e0783beb3c9985ef6d1971","tid":2056180,"uid":257847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a3690c789fc057bd18d71fa64e23a207c0b53ad","tid":2056180,"uid":25112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:00:27.000Z","msg":"Pish 呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感謝"},{"pid":"ed30e6275ef5377791aa07591b9ac0302bb61a49","tid":2056180,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"51acd0df8961ba44a4aa2249975e15aad374bc2a","tid":2056180,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:11:07.000Z","msg":"希望多啲人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05e6a4cd0e9cc60a091024dcba509ca9b96596a","tid":2