ca73aa791b2e81f73d626a8a86c4e250444fe3","tid":2056180,"uid":230196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打好有才華<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:57:38.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:15:41.000Z","msg":"多謝欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9819458514f7bf7bf5145bcd603352815414bd5","tid":2056180,"uid":257847,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:26:49.000Z","msg":"題外話<br />\n自己改呢份詞原意係想大家回想返過去一年既辛酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一年既感覺雖然好長，但係推翻政權、爭取獨立既路從來都唔會係一條短既路。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只希望再過多三五十年，大家仍然可以記得之前所發生大大小小既事、你自己當中經歷過既點滴、同你並肩作戰既一班人、為香港作出貢獻同犧牲既人、同埋無數既淚水血汗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭其實只係啱啱開始，希望大家都可以堅持落去，繼續用自己既方法同力量去重奪我哋應有既自由同權利。而即使最後結局係點都好，都請你唔好忘記曾經付出過既人、背後支持你既人、呢一群真正愛自己家鄉既香港人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6efe3b8737897bdadec93c80b40dc86bb0a2e4","tid":2056180,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:15:59.000Z","msg":"朋友致電 胸口很失儀被送醫<br />\n<br />\n原來呢句唔啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n改做<br />\n朋友致電 說胸口給刺被送醫"},{"pid":"32b5d7867f2bfc34018cb94c387352f09786755d","tid":2056180,"uid":71426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a6efe3b8737897bdadec93c80b40dc86bb0a2e4","tid":2056180,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:15:59.000Z","msg":"朋友致電 胸口很失儀被送醫<br />\n<br />\n原